                                                        <h4 style="text-align: center;margin-top: 25px;color: #008080">Privacy Policy</h4>
                                                        <label style="margin-left:30px;margin-top:15px;margin-right:35px;line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;">We, Cocogen, upholds an individual’s data privacy rights and assures that all your personal data, sensitive personal data and privileged information (collectively, “Personal Data”), collected and to be collected, are processed in compliance to the Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA No. 10173 and its Implementing Rules and Regulations (IRR). </label>

