                                              <label style="margin-left:30px;margin-top:25px;margin-right:35px;line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;"><strong>Use</strong>: The collected personal data shall be used to process your transactions (e.g. insurance quotations and applications, policy issuance, claims servicing, premium payments); communicate and respond to your request; send your statements billings and notices for your insurance coverage; serve as a reference for promotional information regarding our products; conduct surveys and inform through phone, mail, email, SMS or other communication facility in order to help us take better care of your insurance needs and allow us improve our products and services for you; comply with the directives issued by regulatory bodies; assist the Company in risk management, identity and claim verification and prevent and detect fraud; and, perform any other actions as may be necessary to implement the terms and conditions of our contract.</label>

                                              <label style="margin-left:30px;margin-top:25px;margin-right:35px;line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;">We may disclose and share your personal data to the following: </label>

